---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Toolkit" description="Free toolkit for minimums-to-momentum: dashboards, scripts, checklists, and profit tracking.">
  <section class="card">
    <span class="badge">Free toolkit</span>
    <h1 class="h1">The Minimums → Momentum Toolkit</h1>
    <p class="muted">
      No paid upsell. Just the templates and scripts I actually use while climbing out.
      Everything is built for uneven income, multiple bills, and real-life chaos.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="grid" style="margin-top:18px; gap:14px">
    <div class="card">
      <h2 class="h2" style="margin-top:0">Debt Escape Dashboard</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        A weekly view of minimums, must‑pays, buffer, and one momentum move.
        Built to keep you out of “surprise week” territory.
      </p>
      <ul class="muted" style="margin:0; padding-left:18px">
        <li>Balances + minimums table</li>
        <li>Due date calendar view</li>
        <li>Leak tracker and weekly momentum log</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2 class="h2" style="margin-top:0">Call Scripts Pack</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        Scripts for APR reductions, fee waivers, and hardship options.
        Includes logging prompts so each call becomes a measurable attempt.
      </p>
      <ul class="muted" style="margin:0; padding-left:18px">
        <li>APR reduction script + objections</li>
        <li>Hardship terms checklist</li>
        <li>Call outcome log</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2 class="h2" style="margin-top:0">Gig Profit Tracker</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        A simple calculator method for turning gross into real net, so you know
        what you can actually assign toward debt or buffer.
      </p>
      <ul class="muted" style="margin:0; padding-left:18px">
        <li>Gas + maintenance estimate</li>
        <li>Tax set‑aside percentage</li>
        <li>Net‑to‑goal assignment rule</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="card" style="margin-top:18px">
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-top:0">How to get it</h2>
    <p class="muted">
      I’m finishing the packaging. If you want early access or to beta test the toolkit,
      send a quick note.
    </p>
    <a class="focusable" href="mailto:hello@enoughtoevolve.com"><b>Email for early access →</b></a>
    <div class="muted" style="margin-top:10px">You’ll only hear from me when the toolkit is ready.</div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
